description:
This week’s episode of Unqualified starts off with a very special announcement from Sim and Amy as well as some incredible feedback from our dear listeners. Then, the wonderfully talented actor and filmmaker Zach Braff (SCRUBS, GARDEN STATE) joins us (15:22)! First, Anna pitches a new podcast idea to Zach, “Bros Before Hoes” (16:02) and Zach gives us his thoughts on tattoos (18:54). After that, they play a round of “Just Answer” (23:44) and have a conversation on dating within the entertainment industry (30:00). Later, Anna asks Zach what woman he would want to trade places with for a day (35:12) and they discuss what it’s like to work alongside difficult actors (42:52). Finally, they call Annalisa, whose fiancé has been spending time with a friend’s hot ex-girlfriend (49:12), and Liz, whose boyfriend seems to have a wandering eye online (1:11:26). Listen now!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
